{
  "chapter": 27,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十七回\"脱困入困\"讲述了小鱼儿被困洞窟时，一位身穿绿裙、鬓插山茶花的神秘少妇突然出现。她以温柔甜美的言语迷惑献果神君，令其攀绳逃离时因绳中暗藏的毒针中毒坠崖身亡。沈轻虹随后攀绳，绳断坠崖。绿裙少妇与小鱼儿一同跳下绝壑，却用一柄五色大伞安全着陆于崖底一片看似仙境实为死地的谷底。崖上出现一位神秘人物大声威胁，绿裙少妇恐惧万分。二人在谷底发现草地整齐却无尸骨痕迹，树木下半截树皮光滑似有人常摸，暗示此地另有玄机。本章核心是绿裙少妇的登场与骗术展示，以及崖底神秘空间的发现。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "您要我出去，我这就出去，您又何必费这么大的劲，生这么大的气呢。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "老爷子您若喜欢我留在这里，我就留在这里，替你扫地煮饭补衣服……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我看你不如做我的媳妇儿吧。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你若真的肯要我做媳妇，我真开心死了，像你这样又聪明，又英俊的丈夫，我找了十年都没找到，只可惜……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "只可惜什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "只可惜我的年纪太大了，等你三十岁的时候，我已经是老太婆了，那时你又想甩了我，又不忍心，岂不是让你为难么！我又怎忍让你为难呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你不说我年纪太小，只说自己年纪太大，像你这么说话的女子，就算是个杀人不眨眼的母夜叉，我也是喜欢的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不管你说的是真是假，这句话我一定永远记在心里。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "你呢？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我若不喜欢留在此处又当如何？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "老爷子若觉得这里太气闷，想出去逛逛，我已在外面备好了梯子，老爷子您随时都可以走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "嘶声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "老爷子你若还不放心，只管先上去，然后咱们再上，留下这位少爷最后再带着箱子走，这样老爷子既可放心咱们，咱们也可放心老爷子您了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这法子的确再好也没有，别人若先上去，猴老兄必定不放心，此番猴老先上去，也要等着最后一批珠宝上来，必定不会割断绳子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "但你……你真的是完全出于善意么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "text": "老爷子您想想我会有什么恶意呢？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "世上真有你这么好的人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我生来就是这样，只知替别人着想，替别人做事，自己也没法子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xian_guo_shen_jun",
      "speaker_name": "献果神君",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "沈轻虹，你跟着……",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这……这是怎么回事！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这原该问你才是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "莫非是他老人家年纪太大，连绳子都抓不住了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "老实说你这绳子上究竟有何鬼怪？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "这绳子是好好的呀，又没有断，我方才就是从上面下来的么。你若不信，不妨拉拉看。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "这绳子里若是藏着几根毒针，伸手去拉的人滋味一定不大好受。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "不错，这绳里必定暗藏毒针，否则献果神君又怎会松手，不想你这女子竟是如此狠毒，我今日才算开了眼了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你们要如此说，我也没法子，既是如此，我……我只有自己拉给你们瞧吧。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我早已知道你会回来的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我本来已想不管你们，但又实在不忍心，唉！我的心为什么总是这么软，简直连我自己都不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "这绳子究竟是好是坏，如今你们总该知道了吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你若还不相信，不妨用块布包着手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "text": "你莫瞧我，我也没了主意，但是……我想这绳子总该不会断了吧，否则她自己也上不去了。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_qing_hong",
      "speaker_name": "沈轻虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事到如今，无论如何我也要试一试了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你这人究竟是好是坏，到现在我也弄不清了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你……你……你真是个骗死人不赔命的女妖怪。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "哦！是么？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你用绳子里的毒针毒死那老猴子，又将绳子划断一半等着沈轻虹来上当，但以你的武功，你本来不必费这么多心思，就可杀死他们的呀？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "要自己动手杀人，那多没意思，我一生中从未自己动手杀过一个人，全都是别人心甘情愿去死的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "但我还是不明白，绳子断了，你自己怎么上去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这里舒服得很，我已不想上去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "女孩子说的话能叫我猜不透的，你是第一个。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你的朋友被我害死了，你不想报仇？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我打也打不过你，骗也骗不过你，怎么样报仇？何况，正如你所说，这不是你迫着他们，而是他们自己心甘情愿送上门来上当的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你心里不难受？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这两人一个是早已该死了，另一个是十五年前自己就不想活了，如今死得正是对工对路，我又难受个什么！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这样的孩子，我才真是从来没有见过。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "好，现在你可以开始骗我了，骗到我死为止。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "骗死了你，我一个人在这里岂非寂寞得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你……你自己难道真的也不上去了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我又没生翅膀，又不会飞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你真是个女妖怪。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我若是女妖怪，你就是小妖怪。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这倒不错，一个女妖怪，一个小妖怪，在这鬼洞里过上一辈子，将来说不定还会生了一大群小小妖怪……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "姓萧的鬼丫头，你跑不了的，老子已知道你从哪里下去的，老子就在这里等着你，除非你一辈子也不上来。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "他是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他……他不是人，他简直是个老妖怪。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你真那么怕他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不知道，不知道……他做出来的事，世上永远没有人能猜得透的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "姓萧的，你真不上来么？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "好，老子数到十，你若还不上来，等老子捉到你时，担保要你受十天十夜的活罪，若让你少受一刻，老子都不是人。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "看来，他果然有叫人连死都死不了的本事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "现在开始！一！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这厮如此凶恶，莫非是'十大恶人'之一？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "十大恶人若和他比起来，简直就像是最乖的小孩子了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "他比'十大恶人'还狠？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "三！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "他叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不会知道他的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "他既然比'十大恶人'还狠，就应该很有名才是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "咬人的狗是不叫的，你知道么？越是没有名的人才越厉害，他就算做了神鬼难容的事，别人也不知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "四……好，看样子你真的不上来了，你要不要听听老子捉到你时，要如何对付你。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好凶的人，这样的活咸肉，只怕连李大嘴都没有吃过。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你认得李大嘴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你认得他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "在江湖中混的人，谁不知道他？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "五！……你听到了么！五！再数五下，你就要完蛋，你若以为老子捉不到你，你就大错特错了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "罢了。与其等着被他捉住，倒不如现在先死了干净。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你……你怕什么？咱们等在这里不上去，他反正也不敢下来的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你不知道，他说过的话，从来没有不算数的，他若说能够捉住我，就是真的能捉住我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你不能死，你死了我一个人在这里多寂寞。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你还想活么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我活得正有意思，为什么不想活？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他连你也不会放过的……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "六！现在已数到六了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他总有法子捉住你，我若死了，他一定要将气都出在你身上，那时你就更惨了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你要跳下去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "以我看来，你也是和我一齐跳下去的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你要我也跳下去？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我一个人死也寂寞得很，你肯陪陪我么？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "叫人陪着她一齐死，免得她寂寞……嘿！这种要求倒也少见得很。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我是喜欢你，才要你陪我一齐跳下去，否则！否则……你是死是活，我才不管你哩。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "七！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你喜欢我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你是聪明人，你难道瞧不出？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "好！我陪你一齐跳下去！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我非但陪你跳，还要抱着你跳。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好……你很好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "八！还有两下了，臭丫头，你的命已不长久了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你真香……能抱着你死，倒真不错。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真是个可爱的孩子，能被你抱着死，更是件不错的事。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_shang_shen_mi_ren",
      "speaker_name": "崖上神秘人",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "九！臭丫头，你听到了么？老子现在已数到九了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你抱好了么？抱紧些，我就要跳了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你跳吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "死，不知道究竟是何滋味。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你马上就要知道了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "死的滋味如何？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "不错！还不错……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可知道，你是个幸运的人，虽然尝过了死的滋味，却不必真的死了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这……这究竟是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你抬头瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这玩意儿真不错，真不知你是如何想出来的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "小鬼，你现在可以放开手了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "我偏不放开你，你骗得我好苦，我被你骗得差点没发疯，你总该让我多抱抱你，算做补偿。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你这小鬼，你究竟是个聪明人，还是个呆子？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这句话我刚刚还问过自己，我自己也回答不出。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我瞧你呀，是个不折不扣的小呆子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你以为你真骗倒了我？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你自己不知道？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "告诉你，我早就知道你不会死的，所以才陪着你往下跳，你这种人，不像是会自己寻死的人。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "哦！是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "告诉你，世上没有一个人能骗得倒我江小鱼。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我现在才发觉你已不是个孩子，而是个大人，是条男子汉，我几乎从未见过像你这样的男子汉。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我虽然没有死，但到了这里，我又没法子了，现在……我什么事只有依靠你，你可不能抛下我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你只管依靠着我，你绝不会后悔。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真好，我知道我不会选错人的。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你当然没有选错，你选得正确极了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，你现在快想个法子，让咱们离开这鬼地方吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你已想出了法子么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "有法子的，自然有法子的。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，我什么都听你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "什么事不对？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这里少了样东西。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "少了东西？什么东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "那老猴子和沈轻虹两人到哪里去了？飞上天了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他……他们不是已摔死了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "不错，摔死了，但尸身呢？我所有的地方都瞧过，竟瞧不见他们一根骨头，就算是被老虎吃了，也吃得没有这样快呀，何况，这里简直连只猫都没有，哪里会有什么老虎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 490
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真的没有瞧见他们的尸身？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 492,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "没有，简直一根骨头都没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 494
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这见鬼的地方，莫非真的有鬼。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "鬼，哪里会有鬼！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "若没有鬼，那两个人哪里去了？就算他们没有摔死，也该在这里呀，何况，他们是绝对不可能不摔死的。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 508
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这里必定还有别的人。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这鬼地方会有人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 516
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "呀，不错，你不但头脑好，眼睛好……这里既然有人住，我就放心了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但……人呢？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 522,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "人……人……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 524
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我……我简直想都不敢想了，我一想就要打寒噤。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 530,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你不必想，由我来想，我想已足够了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "睡觉吧，好歹睡一觉再说，最好能一睡不醒……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "过来……快过来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你在哪里？你也学会隐身法了么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 556,
      "line_end": 558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我在这里，在这里！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 560,
      "line_end": 560
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你在干什么？拜菩萨？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 566,
      "line_end": 566
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你快过来，瞧瞧这里。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 568,
      "line_end": 568
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "这没有什么呀，不过是……呀，不错，有了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 570,
      "line_end": 570
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你瞧，这树皮像是常常被人用手摸的，人为什么要摸这树皮，显然只有一个解释……这株树必定就是道门。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 574,
      "line_end": 574
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "text": "你不但头脑好，眼睛也不错。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 576,
      "line_end": 576
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_qun_shao_fu",
      "speaker_name": "绿裙少妇",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "谢谢你。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 578,
      "line_end": 578
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有人在家么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 27,
      "line_start": 580,
      "line_end": 580
    }
